{"tid":2223134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Lunch 哥指 學校因他穿校服出席置地廣場睇《蘋果》及去政總遞請願信被停課兩天","createTime":"2020-09-29T14:38:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T02:46:28.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b32714e29643152451b2adec87c4bf9a69cccc75","tid":2223134,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:38:45.000Z","msg":"人稱「Lunch 哥」的中學生 David 在 FB 專頁透露，家長昨（28 日）晚收到校方 Whatsapp ，指 David 以「Lunch 哥星級抗爭團隊」在專頁發起今日（29 日）「和你買樓（南邊圍）」活動，一旦現場衡突，他以「發起人」身份鼓吹恐墮法網。校方又形容他穿校服示威、叫口號、靜坐，會「使學校陷於政治漩渦」，要求立即停止。David 回覆《立場新聞》，指校方以他穿校服出席置地廣場「睇《蘋果》」、到政府總部遞請願信等活動，處分他今、明兩日停課，要求他反思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/lunch-%E5%93%A5-%E8%A2%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E7%BD%B0%E5%81%9C%E8%AA%B2%E5%85%A9%E6%97%A5-%E5%AE%B6%E9%95%B7%E4%BF%A1%E6%8C%87%E7%A9%BF%E6%A0%A1%E6%9C%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81-%E4%BD%BF%E5%AD%B8%E6%A0%A1%E9%99%B7%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%BC%A9%E6%B8%A6/?fbclid=IwAR0-SC9MMxjw6x2G8Tnvx-_ydbzkCMnOlcy69fefh4fhgijxOFTtEH9dkJM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Flunch-%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%259C%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581-%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E9%2599%25B7%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25BC%25A9%25E6%25B8%25A6%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0-SC9MMxjw6x2G8Tnvx-_ydbzkCMnOlcy69fefh4fhgijxOFTtEH9dkJM&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWHljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=38319fc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Flunch-%25E5%2593%25A5-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25AA%25B2%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%2597%25A5-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%259C%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA